label.phrase: to pass judgment judgment will be passed upon you i will stand up for who i am never moved by condemnation no one is placed higher than another no matter race or creed or gender we must teach forgiveness and compassion for all life through understanding of our differences we will find respect for one another we are all flesh and blood i am not afraid to speak my mind no matter the consequences stay true to yourself through the humble eyes of a child we will realize true equality they can not take me from me
